    APIServer -->|"HTTPS/9443<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>Webhook Admission"| WebhookSvc

    %% Controller to API Server
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token"| APIServer

    %% Controller creates ingress resources
    Controller -.->|creates| Route
    Controller -.->|creates| AP
    Controller -.->|creates| EF

    %% Ingress flows
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Edge/Reencrypt"| Route
