    AP --> HTTPRoute

    %% Egress flows
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>NGC API Key"| NGCAPI
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443 or HTTP/80<br/>TLS 1.2+ (configurable)<br/>Bearer Token"| ModelRegSvc

